'''Eye sacks''' were small sacks under [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Eye/Legends|eyes]]. [[Color/Legends|Colored]] blue or sometimes purple, they gave the Yuuzhan Vong the appearance of [[Wikipedia:Dark circles|dark circles]]. They pulsated slightly in response to the Yuuzhan Vong's emotional state. Eye sacks were also considered a mark of beauty among [[Gender/Legends|female]] Yuuzhan Vong; the bluer the sacks, the more attractive.

